				"content1": "2.1 By registering or connecting your wallet on www.{siteName} (the 'Website'), you enter into a binding agreement with {siteName} N.V. and agree to: (i) these Terms and Conditions; (ii) our Privacy Policy; (iii) our Cookie Policy; (iv) our Affiliate Terms; and (v) our Responsible Gaming Policy.",
