					"In the event of conflict, these Terms prevail over any other rules, promotions, or external materials.",
					"Only the English version of these Terms is legally binding. Translations are for convenience only."
				]
			},
			"account": {
				"title": "4. Account, Wallet Login & Security",
				"intro": "{siteName} uses Dynamic.xyz for wallet-based authentication and security measures to protect your account.",
				"walletLogin": {
					"title": "4.1 Wallet Login (Dynamic.xyz)",
					"items": [
