						"Enable any offered platform security features (for example, 2FA for associated services) and secure your own wallet.",
						"Notify support immediately if you suspect unauthorized access."
					]
				}
			},
			"eligibility": {
				"title": "5. Eligibility & User Warranties",
				"intro": "5.1 You represent and warrant that:",
				"items": [
					"You are at least 18 years old (or the minimum legal gambling age in your jurisdiction).",
					"You are legally permitted to use online crypto gambling services where you are located.",
					"You are the lawful owner of the wallet you connect.",
					"You will not use VPNs or location spoofing to bypass regional restrictions.",
					"You will not use the Service for illegal or commercial purposes.",
					"You accept that cryptocurrency value may fluctuate and you bear all market risk."
				],
				"outro": "5.2 If you breach these warranties, {siteName} may suspend or terminate access and withhold funds where permitted by law."
			},
			"restricted": {
				"title": "6. Restricted Jurisdictions",
				"content1": "6.1 {siteName} does not accept players from jurisdictions where crypto gambling is prohibited or restricted. This includes, but is not limited to:",
				"content2": "United States (and U.S. territories), United Kingdom, France, Netherlands, Spain, Germany, Australia, Austria, Comoros, Iran, North Korea, Sudan, Syria, and any jurisdiction listed on FATF blacklists.",
				"content3": "6.2 Attempting to access the Service from a restricted jurisdiction, including via VPN or proxy, is a breach of these Terms and may lead to account closure and forfeiture of funds."
			},
			"crypto": {
				"title": "7. Crypto Deposits & Withdrawals",
				"policy": {
