			"paragraph1": "Responsible gambling means playing for fun, with time and budget limits that fit your lifestyle.",
			"paragraph2": "Recognizing risks early protects both your finances and your well-being.",
			"tips": {
				"0": "Treat gaming as entertainment, not income.",
